Jerry Springer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jerry_Springer 0 Gerald Norman "Jerry" Springer (born February 13, 1944) is an English-born American television presenter, former lawyer, politician, news presenter, actor, and musician. He hosted The Jerry Springer Show, a tabloid talk show, between September 30, 1991 and July 26, 2018 and debuted the Jerry Springer Podcast in 2015.
